WEBVTT

00:07.303 --> 00:11.988
Elvis, the 7-year-old cat, weighs a whopping 16.4 kilograms...

00:12.283 --> 00:14.383
...more than an average 3-year-old child.

00:16.869 --> 00:20.895
He's such a fat feline that his legs struggle to support his weight,...

00:21.422 --> 00:23.723
...so he finds it difficult to even walk.

00:26.097 --> 00:29.653
And the health problems it's causing him mean it's a race against time for...

00:29.789 --> 00:31.691
...his carers to slim him down.

